rComments:
Asynchronous course with a test every Monday covering the previous 2 courses.
Despite my best efforts, I found this course difficult and not very understandable which stressed me out a lot throughout the session. The quizzes were different from the course and there were often traps.

Professor Achab was extraordinarily rude and condescending in one on one interactions. Standoffish, even. The class covered the basics for French. Participation is very important, and you need to show up to most of the lectures. This course is not too difficult if you put in some basic effort. If you want an A though, you need to put in the effort.
